'''''Lothar''''' was an [[CR92a Assassin-class corvette|''Assassin''-class corvette]] (or a similarly modified corvette) and one of several vessels used by clan leader [[Tamaron]]'s [[Airam sector/Legends|Airam]] to deliver supplies to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] in the [[The Drift/Legends|Kuras Drift]]. Unlike the other Airam ships, it carried fuel instead of warheads.

The cargo transfer operation came under [[Mission to Kuras Drift|attack]] by rival Airam clan leader [[Ilay]] and the [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial''-class Star Destroyer]] [[Wasp (Imperial-class)|''Wasp'']]. The ''Lothar'' arrived with the ''Wasp'' in hot pursuit. Unfortunately the [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]] were only able to identify its cargo before it succumbed to the ''Wasp's'' [[Turbolaser/Legends|turbolaser]] batteries.

==Behind the scenes==
*Although the fate of the ''Lothar'' has no impact on the mission in the game, it is technically impossible to successfully complete the mission before the ''Wasp'' destroys the ''Lothar''. The corvette's destruction is thus considered canonical.

